data.description: A Beautiful Brick Home with Modern Upgrades and Sprawling Outdoor Space!  Looking for a spacious home with ample room to live and grow? Look no further! This beautiful brick home sits on an expansive 0.31-acre lot and features four generously sized bedrooms and two full bathrooms. Not to mention, the home boasts a brand-new HVAC system with new ductwork (installed in 2022), upgraded plumbing (completed in 2021 and 2022), and new flooring (added in 2021). Additionally, new garage doors were installed in 2023 and a backyard shed was added in 2019. If you're interested in seeing this stunning property, please call to schedule a private showing today!
